    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The faculty here are so concerned about their students. they always make sure that their students doesn't have any kind of confusion or they need any kind of help etc. every semester they takes feedbacks from the students for knowing the students.",
          "name": "MEDHA VISHWAKARMA",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "In the name of infrastructure, they've created a huge campus along with beautiful surroundings by planting trees everywhere. The infrastructure is so good in sharda university. also there is a battery car who roams here and there in the campus.",
          "name": "MEDHA VISHWAKARMA",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "they provides opportunities to the students by taking them to conferences and giving them placement opportunities. they creates a friendly environment so that students can get comfortable with them and feeling joy to do work.",
          "name": "MEDHA VISHWAKARMA",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "And the history faculty is also quite good.",
          "name": "Aarnav Garg",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "finally, its fee structure it is much high as compared to facilities and also i don't like because they always brings money in every single task.",
          "name": "MEDHA VISHWAKARMA",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus Wi-Fi is abismal and is at times worse than 4G",
          "name": "Aarnav Garg",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The IT department is also not helpful, I contacted them multiple times complaining about the poor Wi-Fi",
          "name": "Aarnav Garg",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "IT department's response was either, \"Try rebooting the device\" or \"Your device is too old get a new one\"",
          "name": "Aarnav Garg",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
